title: Kiri Te Kanawa - Best Of Kiri Te Kanawa (1999)@flac
description:
Dame Kiri Te Kanawa's magnificent soprano breathes a fresh spirit into operatic favorites by Mozart, Puccini and Wagner in this collection of arias and other songs. Per Piate, Ben Mio, O Mio Bambino Caro and Vissi D'Arte are joined by Gustav Holst's In the Bleak Midwinter and the pop classic "The Windmills of Your Mind," among others. 
A diverse and exciting collection from one of the finest voices of our age. (AMG)
